      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 an exceptionally well-preserved used car that stands out even among the best examples on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains a deep, mirror-like shine and bodywork free of dents, scratches, or blemishes of any significance. All trim pieces, glass, and lights are in perfect order. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, headliner, or dashboard surfaces; every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order. Service records support a history of diligent, timely maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that genuinely feels and drives like new, with none of the compromises typically associated with pre-owned ownership.",
      "price": 46000.0,
