      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you an honest, complete picture of what you can expect. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains most of its original luster and color depth, though there are a few minor scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents or structural damage to report, and the body panels are straight and properly aligned. The interior is clean and well-kept, with the upholstery showing moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light scuffing on the door panels, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. All major interior features \u2014 climate control, infotainment, and power accessories \u2014 are functioning as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. The vehicle has been regularly serviced, and the drivetrain feels responsive and solid. The tires have decent tread remaining and the brakes are in good working order. This is a dependable, everyday driver that has been cared for and is ready for continued use without any immediate repair needs.",
